  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nAfter opening the community link all messages at the corresponding chat are read immediately (so chat view is considered as opened) \r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ncan see unread messages from User A\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nmessages from `User A` are read immediately \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/4557972/d48bd148-1e5a-43c5-b5af-e43ad384fe27\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n**Prerequisites:** User A and User B are contacts\r\n1) User A: send community link to User B\r\n2) User B: open the community link and close it\r\n3) User A: send more messages\r\n4) User B: check the chat list\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: 1.23 \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
